</style></head><body class="pdf ko-KR" lang="ko-KR"><article id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c2-a148-f0d34382cc5f" class="page sans"><header><div class="page-header-icon undefined"><span class="icon">👍🏻</span></div><h1 class="page-title" dir="auto">Densely Connected Convolutional Networks</h1><p class="page-description" dir="auto"></p></header><div class="page-body"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b7-9c75-eaf9e2e04437" class="block-color-gray_background">0. Abstract</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8064-85d5-fc58cd7ab3aa"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">📌</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8041-bfb4-c64a85ef7aa4" class="">▪️ 문제 정의 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800b-968e-d7123ccd8640" class="">: 깊은 CNN은 성능이 좋지만 gradient 소실 및 비효율 문제 존재 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-803a-80ac-e5e40ad2554b" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b9-9f34-e99a61f12050" class="">💡 <strong>모든 layer를 연결하는  DenseNet 구조 제안 </strong><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8051-bcd0-c84c47187c5d" class="">➡️ 각 layer를 모든 이전 layer와 연결 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-803f-b65a-ce8522576b7d" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80cc-a87f-ff976b385d93" class="">▪️ 동작 방식 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-802b-8132-c7c73ffb7fb1" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">각 layer는 이전 모든 feature를 입력으로 사용 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b5-8468-eff165a0b98d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">자신의 feature도 이후 layer에 전달</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800b-8cc4-cdf4f658307f" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801e-8fe7-f51ea65ccc78" class="">▪️ 장점 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a1-ae03-f69de12186dd" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">gradient 소실 완화 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-8090-86cc-e73338236a7a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">feature 재사용 증가 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ea-958e-e882a157442e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">파라미터 수 감소  </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-809e-ba96-c9c5807b16d9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"></li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a8-aba4-e7eee694176b" class="">➡️ DenseNet은 <strong>모든 layer를 연결하여 정보 흐름과 학습 효율 개선한 CNN 구조</strong> </p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8015-b830-cb9996cad9d1" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-808d-99e7-ecd12516799c" class="block-color-gray_background">1. Introduction</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ac-a2bd-e845e3bd0f1b" class="block-color-teal_background">이 논문이 다루는 분야 </h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8058-b311-e04959f3db9f"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">📌</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h4 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e7-8b91-eebe94f37ed9" class=""><strong>컴퓨터 비전 (Computer Vision)</strong></h4></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80db-8346-d3a860d66c60" class="">➡️ 이미지 분류를 위한 CNN 구조 설계 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-806a-912b-dad6a2853c26" class="">본 논문은 이미지 인식 문제를 위한 딥 CNN 구조 설계 (네트워크 아키텍처) 분야를 다룬다. </blockquote></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-807d-8b25-cb2f3bf34aac" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-807f-bb2e-f79771f82f23" class="block-color-teal_background">해당 task에서 기존 연구 한계점</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c1-9a45-c3ac558f815b"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">🚨</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h4 id="33f1aa3f-848d-803f-ad3e-f6fe7fcdcc23" class=""><strong>CNN이 깊어질수록 발생하는 정보 전달 및 학습 문제 </strong></h4></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e1-bb22-dbaf7a23fd57" class="">1️⃣ Gradient vanishing 문제 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8082-aa6b-f34432834ea1" class="">: 네트워크가 깊어질수록 gradient 소실</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e5-8858-c31f7b8e7c7c" class="">➡️ 학습이 어려움 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806d-90e6-d3f849a3ac45" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808c-8702-f72153ffcb2c" class="">2️⃣ 정보 전달 손실 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8034-ae88-e5d8b7edf4d5" class="">: 깊은 layer로 갈수록 초기 정보가 희석되거나 사라짐 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8048-8fc9-e416894af095" class="">➡️ 중요한 feature 손실 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80fe-a972-cef070352545" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801a-94d5-eb54bc324a5e" class="">3️⃣ ResNet의 한계 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f9-acc8-cb536ceeeb5b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">feature 재사용 비효율 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-8093-b81d-d83d6aa4e5f7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">불필요한 layer 존재 가능 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f2-9ec2-dc21d41a908f" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80fe-a142-da3cc706b5a4" class="">4️⃣ 파라미터 비효율 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8085-b473-e75112a53981" class="">: layer마다 새로운 feature를 생성해 중복 feature 생성</p></div></div></p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800d-8701-cdf7ceb010c2" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-809e-adb8-cdec56ccfaf9" class="block-color-teal_background">논문의 contributions</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8080-ad18-f9e0cfd0fd61"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">💡</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h4 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80d5-afd8-dad5d0cd39c8" class=""><strong>모든 layer를 연결하는 Dense Connectivity 구조 제안 </strong></h4></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8097-a95d-c800fbbea2cf" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8010-ba7e-cd47a787f770" class="">1️⃣ Dense Connection 구조<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ff-80c5-ef15a4e6c711" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">각 layer를 이전 모든 layer와 연결</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b4-b0e3-ed1bfb8f0c3e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">기존 CNN과 달리 feature를 누적(concatenation) 방식으로 전달</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8034-9c53-e3a2139b32e8" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a9-a934-f987f92b1f03" class=""> 2️⃣ Feature 재사용<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8056-9075-f4cef64dd6c4" class="">: 이전 layer의 feature를 계속 활용</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8021-bb1b-f6780989ebc3" class="">➡️  중복 feature 생성 감소</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808c-8a51-f38e23bb0b1c" class="">➡️ 표현 효율 향상</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80bf-b9ff-ecd512bb911b" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-803c-8945-fd2a744c2603" class="">3️⃣ Gradient 흐름 개선<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-802a-ad1f-e846210b4d78" class="">: layer 간 직접 연결을 통해 gradient vanishing 문제 완화</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-805c-878b-ecb32063e361" class="">➡️ 깊은 네트워크 학습 안정성 증가</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8061-b918-cc75348bce79" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c1-b295-f72016c8e0bf" class=""> 4️⃣ 파라미터 효율성<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80de-83e1-d355ac39ffcf" class="">: 불필요한 feature 생성 감소</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e3-b6ac-f88c101481e4" class="">➡️ 더 적은 파라미터로 높은 성능 달성</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8052-805c-decd2855d6a6" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-8033-a294-e5244e0f2665" class="">DenseNet은 <strong>layer 간 dense connection을 통해 feature 재사용과 gradient 흐름을 개선</strong>하여 효율적인 CNN 구조를 제안 </blockquote></div></div></figure></div></div></article></body></html>